  "body": "### Overview\r\nWhen profiling gas consumption, it should be possible to run all contract calls as transactions.\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\nThe logic to do this already exists for coverage evaluation so implementing it shouldn't be hard.  The `--gas` flag can be expanded to have 2 modes:\r\n\r\n* the current approach where nothing changes, but a report is shown at the end\r\n* the new approach where all calls are handled as transactions, then immediately reverted\r\n\r\nI'm not sure what the CLI syntax should be at this time.",
